                </button>
                <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right">
                    <li><a href="javascript:$('#searchOrg').attr('placeholder', '本校组织')">本校组织(默认)</a></li>
                    <li><a href="javascript:$('#searchOrg').attr('placeholder', '所有组织')">所有组织</a></li>
